author: Al Jazeera
title: Trump, aides flirt with China lab coronavirus conspiracy theory
description: But experts overwhelmingly say analysis of COVID-19's genome rules out the possibility it was engineered by humans.
content:
President Donald Trump and some officials are flirting with a theory that coronavirus was set loose on the world by a Chinese lab that let it escape.
